snippet.title: Adventures of Batman & Robin | Game Gear Longplay
snippet.description:
The Adventures of Batman & Robin | Game Gear Longplay - Full Playthrough/ Gameplay

I was patient enough to play it... I doubt anyone will be patient enough to watch it. There's a reason the GG version is almost never mentioned.
